<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Know Us | Association des Scouts du Petit Ange</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" href="assets/icon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #003366;
      --secondary-color: #f7f9fc;
      --accent-color: #3B82F6;
      --text-color: #333;
    }
    body {
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      font-family: 'Tajawal', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-color);
    }
    .navbar {
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }
    .navbar a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .navbar a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-color);
    }
    .navbar .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero-section {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8), rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8)), url('https://source.unsplash.com/random/1600x900/?scouts') no-repeat center center/cover;
      color: white;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .hero-section p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 15px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .about-section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background-color: white;
    }
    .about-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-section h2::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 50px;
      height: 3px;
      background-color: var(--accent-color);
      margin: 20px auto 0;
    }
    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .team-section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    }
    .team-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .team-section h2::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 50px;
      height: 3px;
      background-color: var(--accent-color);
      margin: 20px auto 0;
    }
    .team-member {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .team-member:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    .team-member img {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 5px solid white;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .team-member:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    .team-member h5 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .team-member p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }
    .social-icons {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .social-icons a {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .social-icons a:hover {
      color: var(--accent-color);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Association des Scouts du Petit Ange</h1>
      <p>Empowering young minds, fostering leadership, and building a brighter future through scouting adventures and community service.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        At Association des Scouts du Petit Ange, we are dedicated to empowering young minds and fostering a spirit of teamwork, leadership, and community service. 
        With years of experience and countless success stories, we take pride in our mission to make a positive impact on the lives of young people and our community.
        Through exciting adventures, skill-building activities, and meaningful projects, we help shape the leaders of tomorrow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>